      "patchset_number": 6,
      "line": 18,
      "message": "directories prior to tca-gen2 are still owned by root user, best to remove highlighted part and add -R flag to chmod to chmod them recursively.\nSame as above, u+rwx should suffice, unless something later uses onap user defined in integration image.",
